desc: The best quality once fired brass cases for all of your reloading needs. Streamline your reloading and prevent common reman issues by using our high quality, precleaned, roll sized, pressure checked cases. They’ve been deprimed, swaged, full length sized, chemically washed, and polished in fine corn cob.

layout.text: Our impeccable processing quality control ensures your time spent reloading is a breeze.
